1.Write a MongoDB query to sort customer details in ascending order of their name.
==================================================================================

> db.CUSTOMER.find().sort({Name:1})

{ "_id" : ObjectId("648173d7a10548dc9c1dec3b"), "Name" : "Aleefa", "city" : "alappuzha", "phno" : "9544358026", "age" : 21 }
